text: David Lynch (born 1946) is an American film director. David Lynch may also refer to: *David Lynch (wine expert), American writer and wine expert *David Lynch, American singer formerly with The Platters *David Lynch, co-founder of the American Front *Dave Lynch (1902–1958), Australian rules footballer ==See also== *David Lynch Scott (1845–1924), Canadian lawyer and judge
title: David Lynch (disambiguation)
